document_data.name: Halaema Nightstar
document_data.mainbody: '''Halaema Nightstar''' was a female [[moon elf]] from [[Leuthilspar]].
document_data.Description: Like her sister [[Saelihn Nightstar|Saelihn]], Halaema was youthful, bright, and resourceful.
document_data.History: In [[1367 DR]], she lead [[House Nightstar]] along with her twin sister Saelihn.
